        public UserInputs​(int currentAge,
                  int maxAge,
                  double inflation,
                  double deposits,
                  boolean real,
                  double withdrawals,
                  int retirementage,
                  double equity,
                  double principal)
        Parameters:
        currentAge - int, User Age at present day
        maxAge - int, Maximum age to allow the simulation to run, safety margin
        inflation - double, expected annual inflation rate
        deposits - double, money the user plans to deposit every year
        real - boolean, true use today's money
        withdrawals - double, money user needs per year after retirement
        retirementage - int, age in which the user plans to retire
        equity - double, percentage of equity in the portfolio
        principal - double, initial money at present age
